# WanderUI ✈️

A modern travel booking website UI showcasing destination listings, itineraries, and a smooth booking flow with a visually rich, premium design.

## 🚀 Features
- Browse popular destinations with images and details
- View sample itineraries and trip packages
- Booking flow UI (dates, travelers, search)
- Responsive design for mobile and desktop
- Clean, modern aesthetic with smooth animations

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- React, Vite, CSS / Tailwind CSS

