## ⚙️ Setup Instructions

1. Clone the repository
```bash
git clone <your-repo-link>
cd wanderui
```

2. Install dependencies
```bash
npm install
```

3. Run the app
```bash
npm run dev
```

4. Open `http://localhost:5173` in your browser

